OL,3,CCMAT calls out body-shamers after
OL,4,Cnegative comments on Big Weekend video
OL,6,FIrish singer-songwriter CMAT has hit
OL,7,Fout at body-shamers after the disabled
OL,8,Fcomments on a video of her performance
OL,9,Fat Radio 1's Big Weekend due to
OL,10,Fnegative comments about her weight.
OL,12,FCMAT, who performed in Luton on Sunday
OL,13,Falongside the likes of Coldplay and
OL,14,FRaye, said the BBC turned off comments
OL,15,Fon the video "because so many people
OL,16,Fcalled me fat".
OL,18,FThe video showed the country singer
OL,19,Ftaking off her shirt during her set at
OL,20,FStockwood Park to reveal a more
OL,21,Ffitted, all-white look.
