OL,6,FIt was captioned: "CMAT always gives
OL,7,Fus a fashion moment", but body-shamers
OL,8,Fwere quick to jump into the comments
OL,9,Fand post abusive comments.
OL,11,FCalling out the trolls, CMAT - whose
OL,12,Freal name is Ciara Mary-Alice Thompson
OL,13,F- wrote: "I didn't realise it was
OL,14,Fillegal to have a huge ass!"
OL,16,FHer thread on X continued: "I am
OL,17,Fguilty as charged. It is time to lock
OL,18,Fme up and throw away the key.
