OL,6,F"By the way, I am an award-winning
OL,7,Fsongwriter that has released two
OL,8,Falbums which were received to
OL,9,F'universal acclaim'."
OL,11,FCMAT said a separate video, from the
OL,12,FBrits ceremony, had also gone viral on
OL,13,FTikTok in South America.
OL,15,F"Now people are calling me fat in
OL,16,FSpanish," she added.
OL,18,FFans were quick to defend the singer,
OL,19,Fdescribing her as "fabulous" and a
OL,20,F"legend".
