OL,6,FOne wrote in response to CMAT's post
OL,7,Fon X: "I was at Big Weekend and you
OL,8,Flooked - and sounded - amazing."
OL,10,FThe 28-year-old has risen to success
OL,11,Fin recent years, with her 2022 debut
OL,12,Falbum If My Wife New I'd Be Dead,
OL,13,Fhitting number one in the Irish Albums
OL,14,FChart.
OL,16,FShe was also nominated for best
OL,17,Finternational artist at the Brit
OL,18,FAwards in March.
OL,20,FITV News has approached BBC Radio 1
OL,21,Ffor comment.
