OL,6,FThe country pop singer also announced
OL,7,Fshe will pull out of her performance
OL,8,Fat Latitude Festival due to the
OL,9,Fevent's sponsor's Barclays.
OL,11,FCampaigners have condemned the bank
OL,12,Ffor its investment in companies
OL,13,Fproviding Israel with weapons during
OL,14,Fits war in Gaza.
OL,16,FMore than 100 artists pulled out of
OL,17,FBrighton's Great Escape Festival in
OL,18,FMay over the same issue.
