OL,6,FCMAT said in an Instagram statement:
OL,7,F"I made Latitude aware of what my
OL,8,Fdecision would be weeks ago, but was
OL,9,Fhoping with all of the press
OL,10,Fsurrounding the brave artists who
OL,11,Fpulled out of The Great Escape
OL,12,Ffestival for the same reasons, that
OL,13,FLatitude would divest from Barclays.
OL,15,F"This has not happened and it has been
OL,16,Fmade clear to me that it will not
OL,17,Fhappen.
OL,19,F"I will not allow my precious work, my
OL,20,Fmusic, which I love so much, to get
OL,21,Finto bed with violence."
